Privacy Policy
Plain English Version of Our Privacy Policy
mindsnap LLC ("Us" or "We") provides the mindsnap.app website, quiz.mindsnap.app website and the MindSnap iOS application (collectively, the "Service") to you, the user ("You" or "User"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information about you, as well as the choices you have with respect to this information. It is important that you read this Privacy Policy in conjunction with our Terms of Service. We value the trust you place in us by using our services, and we commit to protecting your personal information.
Information We Collect and How We Use It
Our primary goal in collecting information is to provide and improve our Services, administer your use of the Services, and ensure an enjoyable and easy interaction with our Services. Hereâ€™s how we handle your information:
Account and Interaction Information
: We collect "Personally Identifiable Information" such as your email address when you sign up for our Services. This information helps us provide you with personalized and efficient service. We may also collect information when you contact our support service or interact with our Services in other ways.
Technical, Usage, and Location Information
: Each time you visit our Service, we may collect non-identifying information such as your browser type, operating system, and Internet Service Provider. We use this information to improve and optimize our Services.
Cookies
: We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your interaction with our Service. These technologies help us remember your preferences for your next visit and understand your interactions with our Services, which helps us tailor our offerings to better suit your needs.
How We Use Your Information
To provide, maintain, and improve our Services.
To prevent or address service errors or technical issues.
To fulfill requests you may make or to assist you in using our Services.
To communicate with you, respond to your inquiries, and send you updates about new services and offers.
How We Share and Disclose Information
We do not sell your data, individually or aggregated.
We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our Services. These providers have access to your information only to perform tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for other purposes.
Legal requirements may require us to share your information with authorities or in response to legal processes.
Your Data Rights and Choices
You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time.
You can opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us by using the unsubscribe link in such emails or contacting us directly.
You may manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings, though this may affect how our Services function.
In order to delete or update your personal information please contact us at
contact@mindsnap.app
Security of Your Information
We take the security of your information seriously and implement reasonable precautions to protect it from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no security system is impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee the security of our databases.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes to our information practices. If we make any material changes, we will notify you by email or by means of a notice on our Service prior to the change becoming effective.
Contact Us
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our treatment of your information, please contact us at
contact@mindsnap.app
Children's Privacy
Our Service is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete such information from our files as soon as possible.
Your Consent
By using our Service, you consent to our collection, use, and sharing of your information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.